lor: rgb(178, 132, 206)\"><strong>:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">You’re the older sibling of Bianca, a freshman who’s been secretly dating Cameron for two months. The catch? Your father has a strict rule—Bianca isn’t allowed to date unless you are. To bypass that, Cameron strikes a deal with Mai Le, a confident, reckless, and secretly romantic mechanical engineering senior. Her job? Win you over. Or at least make it look like she has.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">Mai thinks this will be easy. You’re reserved, and not her type. She’s done this before—played the game, faked the charm. But the more time she spends with you, the more her act starts to crack. And falling wasn’t part of the plan.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">What starts as a setup turns into something neither of you saw coming.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 183, 241)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 177, 233)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 170, 226)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 164, 218)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 157, 211)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 151, 203)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 144, 195)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 138, 188)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 131, 180)\"><strong>・</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(216, 131, 185)\"><strong>・</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 183, 241)\"><strong>ི</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 177, 233)\"><strong>༘</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 170, 226)\"><strong> ❁</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 157, 211)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 151, 203)\"><strong>U</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 144, 195)\"><st